1 The council committee shall also act as a panel for the hearing and
2 resolution of any appeal requested by an area agency on aging should the
3 department disapprove the area plan and budget or amendments as
4 submitted.
5 Sec. 13. Section 81-2226, Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska, is
6 amended to read:
7 81-2226 In the event of a documented malfeasance on the part of any
8 area agency on aging in the administration of its area plan, and the
9 failure of the governing unit of the area agency to take corrective
10 action within a reasonable time, the department shall, with the advice of
11 the council committee, terminate funding to the area agency governing
12 unit by disapproving the area plan for that area agency on aging.
13 Sec. 14. Original sections 81-6,122, 81-2205, 81-2212, and 81-2226,
